item.description: Thursday - 2020-07-18 Woke up at 5:50 AM. Had slept at 10:30 the night before - but was in bed by 9:45. That helped. Absolutely obliterated the partner at Othello. He declared me too competitive. Exercise. Hair wash day! Smoothie for breakfast. Thanks to SSJ for the suggestion. Game changing! Wearing all black to work. Interesting look! Work is chaotic. Too much to do! Need to hone down and focus. Trying our Morgen - alt to Akiflow.
